Package: framerrr
Title: Framework That Increases Portability Decreases Maintenance Errors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mick",
           family = "Mioduszewski",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mick@mioduszewski.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8479-9336"))
Description: Framerrr makes it easier to prevent bugs when porting between
environments by separating enironment dependent information in configuration
files. Files paths are logical and not hardcoded physically. Provides helper
functions easing common problems in cross-environment software.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to
    pick a license
